    <briefdescription>
<para>Stretch bar input element with pictogram support. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>Displays a progress/scroll bar using pictograms with variable fill levels.</para>
<para><parameterlist kind="templateparam"><parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>TPictoset</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
